<plot>The sitcom "Lukas" takes place in a big urban flat in Cologne. But behind this bourgeois facade, a fight among three generations, personified by grandfather, father and daughter, takes place. There is one thing all the family members have in common: their inherited stubbornness.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?347066</url></doc>
